moraine (0.1.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * FTP credentials via RCLONE_FTP_* environment (not argv).
  * Optional strict SSH host-key checking (strict_host_key).
  * Form validation feedback; schedule range validation; skip schedules
    with missing targets on install.

 -- Jonaz Thern <info@thern.io>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 21:00:00 +0200

moraine (0.1.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Security: validate target names (path traversal, FTP option injection),
    sanitize server-supplied restore trees, owner-only init/export files,
    nmcli id argument, SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH support.
  * Fix schedule-creation crash, SSH restore tree parsing, incremental
    rclone backups in the GUI, failure logging, prune concurrency guard.

 -- Jonaz Thern <info@thern.io>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 16:00:00 +0200

moraine (0.1.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Per-target VPN, start-at-login, GTK theming fixes.
  * Security hardening: owner-only config/log (0600), private SSH_ASKPASS
    dir, no secrets in argv, rsync --protect-args, injection-safe scheduling.

 -- Jonaz Thern <info@thern.io>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200

